00:01:28,900 --> 00:01:35,980
=Prosecution Elite=
(Key Project of the Supreme People's Procuratorate.)

14
00:01:36,100 --> 00:01:38,420
=Episode 23=

15
00:01:39,086 --> 00:01:40,805
Huiquan always does things
unintentionally, huh?

16
00:01:41,605 --> 00:01:42,805
You guys suppressed the heat
surrounding Zhang Xiaobei,

17
00:01:42,885 --> 00:01:46,686
Shi Xiaohu, and the other victims
of the Huiquan Games.

18
00:01:47,046 --> 00:01:49,086
I'm sure you did it for
Huiquan Corporation unintentionally.

19
00:02:06,020 --> 00:02:08,980
(Meinian Square)

20
00:02:10,846 --> 00:02:11,766
An Ni!

21
00:02:15,805 --> 00:02:16,605
Xiaoting, what's the matter?

22
00:02:16,645 --> 00:02:18,046
You wanted to see me urgently.

23
00:02:18,286 --> 00:02:19,085
An Ni,

24
00:02:19,406 --> 00:02:21,846
I know you guys are busy preparing
for the prosecution.

25
00:02:21,926 --> 00:02:23,926
I shouldn't interrupt you
at this moment.

26
00:02:24,245 --> 00:02:25,365
But I can't hold it in anymore.

27
00:02:25,406 --> 00:02:26,406
I have to tell you.

28
00:02:26,525 --> 00:02:26,926
It's okay.

29
00:02:26,926 --> 00:02:28,046
Tell me what's going on.

30
00:02:28,966 --> 00:02:29,566
An Ni,

31
00:02:29,966 --> 00:02:33,525
I just found a photo of my dad
with another woman in his study room.

32
00:02:34,245 --> 00:02:35,326
His photo with another woman?

33
00:02:36,286 --> 00:02:38,085
Do you know her?

34
00:02:38,126 --> 00:02:39,126
I don't.

35
00:02:39,206 --> 00:02:40,645
She looks familiar to me,

36
00:02:40,645 --> 00:02:42,245
but I can't remember who she is.

37
00:02:43,805 --> 00:02:44,326
So,

38
00:02:44,406 --> 00:02:45,966
are you suspecting your father?

39
00:02:47,046 --> 00:02:48,486
It's not that I don't want to trust him.

40
00:02:48,805 --> 00:02:50,445
It's just that he's untrustworthy.

41
00:02:50,566 --> 00:02:51,365
An Ni, do you know something?

42
00:02:51,486 --> 00:02:54,165
He was whispering to Yin Huiquan last night.

43
00:02:54,445 --> 00:02:55,885
They talked about Zhang Xiaobei.

44
00:02:55,885 --> 00:02:57,005
They even wanted to punish him.

45
00:02:57,885 --> 00:02:58,966
They were too much.

46
00:02:59,326 --> 00:03:01,365
An Ni, I told you this before.

47
00:03:01,525 --> 00:03:02,966
If there's something wrong with Huiquan,

48
00:03:03,046 --> 00:03:04,645
I'll definitely get to
the bottom of this for the sake of

49
00:03:04,645 --> 00:03:06,046
victims like Shi Xiaohu
and Zhang Xiaobei.

50
00:03:06,286 --> 00:03:07,566
Shi Xiaohu is dead.

51
00:03:07,885 --> 00:03:09,085
Zhang Xiaobei is still alive.

52
00:03:09,126 --> 00:03:11,486
I won't allow them
to harm Zhang Xiaobei anymore.

53
00:03:12,486 --> 00:03:14,846
However, if the result of your investigation

54
00:03:15,005 --> 00:03:16,286
shows that there's nothing wrong
with Huiquan,

55
00:03:16,406 --> 00:03:17,926
I can issue a public apology.

56
00:03:19,566 --> 00:03:20,046
An Ni,

57
00:03:20,206 --> 00:03:22,245
you're the only person
I trust right now.

58
00:03:24,126 --> 00:03:25,165
I understand

59
00:03:25,206 --> 00:03:26,206
what you're trying to get here.

60
00:03:27,005 --> 00:03:28,686
But I hope that you won't act recklessly

61
00:03:28,805 --> 00:03:29,805
when it comes to this.

62
00:03:29,805 --> 00:03:30,885
You must trust the law.

63
00:03:31,206 --> 00:03:32,725
We will protect Zhang Xiaobei as well.

64
00:03:32,846 --> 00:03:35,085
Although I don't represent the law,

65
00:03:35,326 --> 00:03:37,846
as a judicial personnel,

66
00:03:38,046 --> 00:03:39,885
I won't let off any crooks

67
00:03:40,046 --> 00:03:41,885
or malign any innocent people.

68
00:03:43,980 --> 00:03:45,460
(Inpatient Department)

69
00:03:53,846 --> 00:03:54,846
Hello, Xiaobei.

70
00:03:56,805 --> 00:03:59,326
I think An Ni should've told you this by now.

71
00:03:59,645 --> 00:04:01,046
Stop bothering me and my father.

72
00:04:01,046 --> 00:04:02,645
My father is running out of time.

73
00:04:03,645 --> 00:04:05,566
You didn't behave like this

74
00:04:05,605 --> 00:04:06,605
when you texted me.

75
00:04:07,085 --> 00:04:08,365
What's with the change in attitude?

76
00:04:09,686 --> 00:04:10,966
Times have changed.

77
00:04:11,286 --> 00:04:13,165
I no longer want to get myself
involved with these matters.

78
00:04:13,605 --> 00:04:15,126
Even so,

79
00:04:15,206 --> 00:04:18,126
are you going to forget about the incident
with Shi Xiaohu just like this?

80
00:04:20,205 --> 00:04:21,886
Shi Xiaohu took his own life.

81
00:04:22,006 --> 00:04:23,406
Those who gave out illegal loans

82
00:04:23,406 --> 00:04:24,606
were already arrested.

83
00:04:25,606 --> 00:04:26,485
Don't tell me you think

84
00:04:26,606 --> 00:04:28,245
that the matter will end just like this?

85
00:04:28,406 --> 00:04:29,525
Don't you think everything

86
00:04:29,525 --> 00:04:30,525
is related to Huiquan?

87
00:04:31,805 --> 00:04:35,286
All this while, news regarding
Shi Xiaohu and you

88
00:04:35,525 --> 00:04:36,325
were suppressed immediately

89
00:04:36,325 --> 00:04:38,606
if they were detrimental
to Huiquan's reputation.

90
00:04:38,645 --> 00:04:39,686
Have you never considered

91
00:04:39,805 --> 00:04:40,846
why they did so?

92
00:04:41,446 --> 00:04:42,645
It's a huge enterprise.

93
00:04:43,126 --> 00:04:44,085
Isn't it normal for them

94
00:04:44,085 --> 00:04:45,286
to deal with a PR crisis like this?

95
00:04:45,606 --> 00:04:47,286
You work for the media.
Don't you know this too?

96
00:04:48,645 --> 00:04:49,446
Of course I know.

97
00:04:50,286 --> 00:04:52,286
You'll testify against
Qian Tianxin in court.

98
00:04:53,286 --> 00:04:55,566
And, we know what you did in Country F.

99
00:04:55,686 --> 00:04:56,765
You're very brave.

100
00:04:56,886 --> 00:04:58,085
I'm impressed by your bravery.

101
00:04:58,805 --> 00:05:00,566
However, why are you unwilling
to go even further

102
00:05:00,686 --> 00:05:03,085
and reveal all of Huiquan's dirty secrets?

103
00:05:03,645 --> 00:05:06,286
I know something's wrong with Huiquan.

104
00:05:06,525 --> 00:05:08,126
But I have no evidence.

105
00:05:08,606 --> 00:05:09,846
Huiquan Corporation is definitely related

106
00:05:09,925 --> 00:05:10,925
to the incident with Qian Tianxin.

107
00:05:11,525 --> 00:05:13,006
Zhao Jikai and Li Yitang too.

108
00:05:13,606 --> 00:05:15,805
They caused Shi Xiaohu's death.

109
00:05:15,925 --> 00:05:17,765
And now, they act
as if nothing had happened.

110
00:05:19,205 --> 00:05:20,205
Justice doesn't exist.

111
00:05:27,525 --> 00:05:28,805
(When you're watching my show)

112
00:05:28,886 --> 00:05:30,205
(in front of your computer,)

113
00:05:30,286 --> 00:05:31,485
(have you ever considered)

114
00:05:31,645 --> 00:05:33,886
that your personal details
and related data

115
00:05:34,126 --> 00:05:37,446
(might be used by criminals
as a tool to hurt you?)

116
00:05:37,686 --> 00:05:40,925
(For example, Huiquan Corporation,
which spent a lot of effort)

117
00:05:41,006 --> 00:05:45,286
(to suppress the incident of Zhang Xiaobei.)

118
00:05:46,045 --> 00:05:47,925
(They didn't spend their energy and capital)

119
00:05:48,006 --> 00:05:49,726
(on how to create products)

120
00:05:49,805 --> 00:05:51,126
(that their users would love)

121
00:05:51,126 --> 00:05:52,726
(in an efficient manner.)

122
00:05:53,606 --> 00:05:56,045
(Instead, they used it
to deceive their users.)

123
00:05:56,205 --> 00:05:57,686
(They used their power)

124
00:05:57,805 --> 00:05:59,446
(to suppress and delete comments)

125
00:05:59,446 --> 00:06:01,205
(that were deemed detrimental to them.)

126
00:06:04,980 --> 00:06:07,820
(Huiquan)

127
00:06:08,045 --> 00:06:10,045
I called you two here today

128
00:06:10,205 --> 00:06:13,325
to deliver a piece of bad news.

129
00:06:15,006 --> 00:06:17,205
The company that's in the middle of a deal with us,

130
00:06:17,446 --> 00:06:19,045
Kaili International Investments,

131
00:06:19,045 --> 00:06:21,286
called me this morning out of the blue.

132
00:06:21,606 --> 00:06:24,205
They said that their executives

133
00:06:24,286 --> 00:06:25,566
have started to doubt
our company's credibility

134
00:06:25,566 --> 00:06:26,886
due to the rumors surrounding us.

135
00:06:27,485 --> 00:06:28,686
They called to notify me

136
00:06:29,245 --> 00:06:32,365
that they would suspend
their investment.

137
00:06:34,126 --> 00:06:35,166
We discussed the deal for half a year.

138
00:06:35,606 --> 00:06:36,606
Now, they're suspending it?

139
00:06:37,006 --> 00:06:38,446
They do have great timing, huh?

140
00:06:39,085 --> 00:06:39,886
Jikai,

141
00:06:40,606 --> 00:06:42,006
I'm sure you understand

142
00:06:43,286 --> 00:06:44,886
the company's condition the best.

143
00:06:46,286 --> 00:06:47,085
Chairman,

144
00:06:48,286 --> 00:06:49,805
all of those were baseless rumors.

145
00:06:50,325 --> 00:06:51,485
I've already told

146
00:06:51,485 --> 00:06:55,205
Li Yitang to investigate the rumors

147
00:06:55,286 --> 00:06:56,846
and cyber-bullying cases related
to Huiquan Corporation.

148
00:06:57,006 --> 00:06:57,846
We'll hold all of them accountable.

149
00:06:58,006 --> 00:06:59,886
We're sending them
the legal letter today.

150
00:07:01,205 --> 00:07:06,006
And, Luo Jiangxiao's foolish daughter,
Luo Xiaoting,

151
00:07:06,245 --> 00:07:07,846
we must make her pay the price.

152
00:07:08,606 --> 00:07:09,925
Enough.

153
00:07:10,325 --> 00:07:12,085
Don't make the conflict more complicated
than it needs to be.

154
00:07:12,286 --> 00:07:13,406
You guys can get back to work.

155
00:07:19,406 --> 00:07:20,286
You, stay here.

156
00:07:35,006 --> 00:07:35,805
Chairman,

157
00:07:36,286 --> 00:07:38,686
since an incident like this
has happened in the company,

158
00:07:38,846 --> 00:07:40,765
for Huibo,

159
00:07:41,485 --> 00:07:44,045
I think we should temporarily
halt its expansion.

160
00:07:44,205 --> 00:07:45,406
Why must we halt it?

161
00:07:45,606 --> 00:07:48,205
Back then, you were on the right track.

162
00:07:48,925 --> 00:07:50,846
As long as we persevere,

163
00:07:51,205 --> 00:07:53,006
we'll definitely achieve success.

164
00:07:54,126 --> 00:07:57,205
When I did market research,

165
00:07:57,286 --> 00:07:59,886
I realized that there were many foreign
investment companies

166
00:08:00,006 --> 00:08:01,205
that were interested in us.

167
00:08:01,245 --> 00:08:02,886
We don't need to rely on
just one option.

168
00:08:03,045 --> 00:08:04,686
If you give me your permission,

169
00:08:04,846 --> 00:08:05,446
I can...

170
00:08:05,485 --> 00:08:07,765
Just focus on your task.

171
00:08:08,126 --> 00:08:09,925
No matter what,

172
00:08:10,045 --> 00:08:11,726
I'll turn Huibo Broadcasting

173
00:08:12,205 --> 00:08:15,365
into the flagship product of the industry.

174
00:08:16,286 --> 00:08:17,126
Mr. Xiao,

175
00:08:17,606 --> 00:08:22,566
now, the company is betting everything on you.

176
00:08:24,045 --> 00:08:26,045
You mustn't disappoint me.

177
00:08:26,485 --> 00:08:27,686
Chairman, please don't worry.

178
00:08:27,805 --> 00:08:29,045
I will not disappoint you.

179
00:08:31,485 --> 00:08:32,486
What do you mean by you can't do it?

180
00:08:32,966 --> 00:08:34,205
I didn't spend all my money on you

181
00:08:34,406 --> 00:08:36,286
just so you could tell me that.

182
00:08:36,885 --> 00:08:37,406
Do you know

183
00:08:37,406 --> 00:08:38,806
the situation we're in right now?

184
00:08:39,486 --> 00:08:40,486
You know nothing.

185
00:08:41,645 --> 00:08:43,926
The old man is starting to suspect me.

186
00:08:44,525 --> 00:08:45,205
Enough.

187
00:08:45,525 --> 00:08:46,525
I won't waste my breath.

188
00:08:48,606 --> 00:08:51,005
Follow my previous instructions.

189
00:08:51,885 --> 00:08:54,486
Make a clean break when it's necessary.

190
00:08:55,885 --> 00:08:56,685
That's all.

191
00:09:45,046 --> 00:09:45,846
Come in.

192
00:09:53,406 --> 00:09:54,205
Jikai.

193
00:09:54,406 --> 00:09:55,246
That's Mr. Zhao to you.

194
00:09:56,205 --> 00:09:57,406
Please refer to me as Mr. Zhao

195
00:09:57,926 --> 00:09:58,926
when we're in the company.

196
00:10:00,525 --> 00:10:01,966
What's with this photo?

197
00:10:02,406 --> 00:10:03,085
It's nothing.

198
00:10:04,325 --> 00:10:05,166
I'm just tired of it.

199
00:10:05,486 --> 00:10:06,406
That's why I changed it.

200
00:10:12,005 --> 00:10:12,606
Mr. Zhao,

201
00:10:13,205 --> 00:10:15,406
these are the name lists and information
I've organized for you.

202
00:10:15,525 --> 00:10:17,606
We've already included the names

203
00:10:17,645 --> 00:10:19,246
of every production staff for
online programs

204
00:10:19,525 --> 00:10:21,926
such as "Xiaoting Never Stops"

205
00:10:22,046 --> 00:10:24,046
and the names of influencers,

206
00:10:24,125 --> 00:10:25,166
content creators,

207
00:10:25,205 --> 00:10:27,205
and independent media
that spread the rumors.

208
00:10:27,406 --> 00:10:29,246
See if we should send them
the legal letter directly

209
00:10:29,246 --> 00:10:30,325
or make an announcement.

210
00:10:45,726 --> 00:10:46,966
Zhao Jikai, you must be
out of your mind.

211
00:10:47,005 --> 00:10:48,406
What else can you do

212
00:10:48,486 --> 00:10:50,846
besides intimidating these youngsters
with the law?

213
00:10:51,445 --> 00:10:53,046
You're the company's
legal affairs director.

214
00:10:53,325 --> 00:10:54,406
Can you do something innovative
for once?

215
00:10:54,445 --> 00:10:56,046
Do you think the company

216
00:10:56,046 --> 00:10:57,125
needs to get into more trouble now?

217
00:10:57,685 --> 00:10:59,205
Public opinion is unfavorable
against our company.

218
00:10:59,246 --> 00:11:00,565
And now, you want to make the company

219
00:11:00,606 --> 00:11:03,286
an evil capitalist image that exploits people
without any remorse?

220
00:11:10,246 --> 00:11:12,085
Enough. I had enough of you.

221
00:11:12,806 --> 00:11:13,606
Please move out

222
00:11:13,765 --> 00:11:15,005
of my house by today.

223
00:11:15,246 --> 00:11:16,486
I don't wish to see you again.

224
00:11:16,726 --> 00:11:18,272
I no longer want
to be involved with you.

225
00:11:25,645 --> 00:11:26,445
Zhao Jikai.

226
00:11:27,286 --> 00:11:29,205
I'll treat it as if you got up
on the wrong side of the bed.

227
00:12:12,486 --> 00:12:13,926
Didn't I tell you already?

228
00:12:14,445 --> 00:12:15,885
Move out of my house.

229
00:12:16,125 --> 00:12:17,445
Why are you here again?

230
00:12:29,325 --> 00:12:30,005
What is this?

231
00:12:30,205 --> 00:12:31,005
A proposal.

232
00:12:34,286 --> 00:12:35,806
I don't need you
to write a proposal for me.

233
00:12:36,525 --> 00:12:37,325
You don't need to please me

234
00:12:37,406 --> 00:12:38,486
with such a method.

235
00:12:38,926 --> 00:12:40,325
This proposal isn't for you.

236
00:12:41,125 --> 00:12:42,726
This is the proposal I made

237
00:12:42,806 --> 00:12:44,445
to clear Qian Tianxin's name.

238
00:12:49,246 --> 00:12:50,645
I don't understand
what you're talking about.

239
00:12:56,806 --> 00:12:59,046
Are you sure?

240
00:13:00,205 --> 00:13:03,046
Isn't that the cause of your trouble lately?

241
00:13:03,806 --> 00:13:05,726
You couldn't sleep all night long.

242
00:13:06,125 --> 00:13:07,246
You kept sighing,

243
00:13:07,286 --> 00:13:08,286
smoking, and drinking.

244
00:13:08,645 --> 00:13:11,366
Your browser history is filled with tabs

245
00:13:11,406 --> 00:13:14,246
regarding how to clear one's name
after committing cybercrimes

246
00:13:14,406 --> 00:13:17,286
and how to hire lawyers for them.

247
00:13:18,685 --> 00:13:20,166
You can look for me.

248
00:13:20,645 --> 00:13:21,846
When I was in university,

249
00:13:21,926 --> 00:13:24,765
I was a debate expert
who was on par with An Ni.

250
00:13:25,125 --> 00:13:25,926
Li Yitang,

251
00:13:26,846 --> 00:13:28,246
you shouldn't have checked my computer.

252
00:13:34,166 --> 00:13:35,366
I even know

253
00:13:35,565 --> 00:13:36,765
that you went abroad last time

254
00:13:37,486 --> 00:13:40,286
to visit Qian Tianxin in Country F.

255
00:13:42,445 --> 00:13:43,565
Who told you that?

256
00:13:46,125 --> 00:13:47,726
You told Xiao Mu'en that you heard about

257
00:13:47,846 --> 00:13:50,445
An Ni's trip to Country F from me.

258
00:13:51,046 --> 00:13:52,445
But you understand this clearly.

259
00:13:52,806 --> 00:13:55,005
An Ni would never tell anyone about that,

260
00:13:55,005 --> 00:13:55,885
including me.

261
00:13:56,806 --> 00:13:58,806
I checked your flight schedule as well.

262
00:14:00,246 --> 00:14:01,246
Everything was developing

263
00:14:01,325 --> 00:14:03,366
in the direction I didn't hope for.

264
00:14:03,445 --> 00:14:04,606
Was I wrong?

265
00:14:07,606 --> 00:14:08,685
I always thought

266
00:14:09,005 --> 00:14:11,085
that you were a foolish woman
falling in love all the time.

267
00:14:11,406 --> 00:14:12,846
I didn't expect you
