00:26:57,685 --> 00:26:59,405
I made a copy of your case file

548
00:27:00,045 --> 00:27:01,685
to proceed with my research.

549
00:27:02,366 --> 00:27:04,366
I realized that there were many issues

550
00:27:05,366 --> 00:27:07,126
you didn't explain clearly with

551
00:27:07,165 --> 00:27:08,366
the statement you gave
under interrogation.

552
00:27:09,165 --> 00:27:11,565
Now, I'll ask you some
of the questions again.

553
00:27:13,685 --> 00:27:14,486
Please go ahead.

554
00:27:16,486 --> 00:27:18,565
You already said

555
00:27:18,766 --> 00:27:21,766
that you were only a trainer.

556
00:27:21,846 --> 00:27:23,246
That's the truth!

557
00:27:23,606 --> 00:27:24,925
You can answer me

558
00:27:24,966 --> 00:27:25,846
after I finish my question.

559
00:27:28,366 --> 00:27:28,886
You said

560
00:27:29,165 --> 00:27:31,165
you didn't participate
in any of the fraud cases,

561
00:27:31,205 --> 00:27:32,766
and that you didn't succeed
in any of them.

562
00:27:33,285 --> 00:27:33,685
That's right.

563
00:27:34,006 --> 00:27:35,405
That's what I said.

564
00:27:36,285 --> 00:27:37,685
But currently,

565
00:27:37,886 --> 00:27:41,325
according to the evidence

566
00:27:41,366 --> 00:27:44,006
already confirmed from the case files,

567
00:27:44,205 --> 00:27:46,805
your statements were invalid.

568
00:27:47,285 --> 00:27:48,486
According to the evidence,

569
00:27:48,685 --> 00:27:51,205
the fraud cases you participated in
involved huge sums.

570
00:27:52,006 --> 00:27:53,366
And, you've directed many of them too.

571
00:27:53,925 --> 00:27:57,805
You're also the pillar of
the fraud syndicate.

572
00:27:58,006 --> 00:28:02,045
And, all your accomplices and the witnesses

573
00:28:02,085 --> 00:28:03,486
who were coerced by you guys before,

574
00:28:03,966 --> 00:28:05,246
how much did they know?

575
00:28:05,805 --> 00:28:07,126
Will they testify against you?

576
00:28:07,285 --> 00:28:08,205
Have you ever considered that?

577
00:28:08,285 --> 00:28:09,085
Mr. Jin,

578
00:28:09,486 --> 00:28:10,685
what should I do then?

579
00:28:10,886 --> 00:28:11,846
What should I say?

580
00:28:11,925 --> 00:28:13,126
What should I say so that they will

581
00:28:13,165 --> 00:28:14,445
reduce my sentence?

582
00:28:14,565 --> 00:28:15,366
Hu Dewang,

583
00:28:15,925 --> 00:28:18,685
as lawyers, we have rules to follow.

584
00:28:18,766 --> 00:28:20,846
I cannot teach you what to say.

585
00:28:20,966 --> 00:28:23,766
I cannot instigate you
to give false statements.

586
00:28:24,085 --> 00:28:25,766
That's very serious,

587
00:28:25,805 --> 00:28:26,726
do you understand?

588
00:28:27,205 --> 00:28:29,246
Do not bring up that topic again.

589
00:28:29,366 --> 00:28:31,766
If not, both of us will bite off
more than we can chew.

590
00:28:32,405 --> 00:28:33,205
I'm sorry.

591
00:28:34,165 --> 00:28:35,006
Actually,

592
00:28:35,565 --> 00:28:37,766
this is pretty obvious.

593
00:28:38,246 --> 00:28:40,886
You're very clear with what you've done.

594
00:28:41,285 --> 00:28:42,285
The public security bureau
and the People's Procuratorate

595
00:28:42,285 --> 00:28:43,805
aren't just for show too.

596
00:28:43,966 --> 00:28:45,565
They'll get to the bottom of this.

597
00:28:46,766 --> 00:28:47,966
Here's my suggestion.

598
00:28:48,366 --> 00:28:51,366
It's best if you prepare for the worst.

599
00:28:51,445 --> 00:28:52,886
For the crimes you've committed,

600
00:28:52,886 --> 00:28:54,846
you'll receive a minimum sentence
of ten years in prison.

601
00:28:57,205 --> 00:28:58,205
If...

602
00:28:58,565 --> 00:29:00,846
If you can take out the money

603
00:29:00,846 --> 00:29:02,165
and compensate the victims,

604
00:29:02,405 --> 00:29:04,606
the law will be lenient to you.

605
00:29:04,685 --> 00:29:06,685
I don't have that much money.

606
00:29:07,285 --> 00:29:09,165
I'm not the big fish here.

607
00:29:09,205 --> 00:29:10,726
Xin already took everything.

608
00:29:11,006 --> 00:29:13,726
I'm not asking you to return
the full amount to them.

609
00:29:16,445 --> 00:29:17,246
What about this?

610
00:29:17,886 --> 00:29:21,886
I'll discuss this with your backer outside.

611
00:29:22,766 --> 00:29:24,366
We'll try to gather some funds.

612
00:29:24,565 --> 00:29:26,445
At least it'll show your sincerity.

613
00:29:29,606 --> 00:29:32,606
Xin, whom you mentioned just now,

614
00:29:32,766 --> 00:29:34,205
how long have you known her?

615
00:29:39,006 --> 00:29:41,606
We knew each other
since we were in Country A.

616
00:29:41,766 --> 00:29:43,205
That Xin you mentioned,

617
00:29:43,285 --> 00:29:45,726
not only was she involved in the cases
in Country F,

618
00:29:45,886 --> 00:29:49,526
but she was also involved
in the murder cases in Country A.

619
00:29:51,766 --> 00:29:53,366
How many years will she be
sentenced to prison?

620
00:29:54,606 --> 00:29:55,405
What?

621
00:29:56,366 --> 00:29:57,405
Did she treat you well?

622
00:30:00,366 --> 00:30:01,565
I was always her follower.

623
00:30:04,366 --> 00:30:06,085
We don't need to worry about that.

624
00:30:06,085 --> 00:30:07,405
Here's my suggestion.

625
00:30:07,486 --> 00:30:10,205
No matter if it's Country A or F,

626
00:30:11,366 --> 00:30:13,966
you have clues that the police

627
00:30:13,966 --> 00:30:15,766
and the prosecutors don't.

628
00:30:15,846 --> 00:30:18,246
If you have any corrections
to make to the situation,

629
00:30:18,366 --> 00:30:19,606
you can do it anytime.

630
00:30:24,606 --> 00:30:26,805
Your beloved instructed me

631
00:30:26,966 --> 00:30:30,805
to tell you that they're doing well out there.

632
00:30:31,966 --> 00:30:34,246
She's very thankful to your friends

633
00:30:34,285 --> 00:30:35,805
who are taking care of her
and your children.

634
00:30:36,565 --> 00:30:39,045
She said she doesn't want to
owe people any favors.

635
00:30:39,085 --> 00:30:41,085
She wants you to repay the favor
when it's possible.

636
00:30:43,366 --> 00:30:44,366
Thank you, Mr. Jin.

637
00:30:49,805 --> 00:30:50,526
I forgot something.

638
00:30:50,646 --> 00:30:51,405
By the way,

639
00:30:51,646 --> 00:30:54,646
she told me that you told her

640
00:30:55,565 --> 00:30:58,726
that Xin was only one of the underlings.

641
00:30:58,846 --> 00:31:00,126
You said that she had a superior.

642
00:31:00,246 --> 00:31:02,726
I think it was an old man.

643
00:31:04,165 --> 00:31:05,685
She said you heard that.

644
00:31:05,966 --> 00:31:07,165
Was that true?

645
00:31:13,486 --> 00:31:14,045
Yes.

646
00:31:16,085 --> 00:31:16,685
Hu Dewang,

647
00:31:16,966 --> 00:31:17,405
you...

648
00:31:18,045 --> 00:31:19,246
Look at you.

649
00:31:19,246 --> 00:31:20,846
Where do I start?

650
00:31:20,846 --> 00:31:23,445
When I came in, I told you

651
00:31:23,846 --> 00:31:25,165
to confess everything

652
00:31:25,205 --> 00:31:27,006
so that we could strive for leniency
upon your sentence.

653
00:31:28,085 --> 00:31:30,165
What are you worried about?

654
00:31:30,285 --> 00:31:31,805
This is an important clue, you know?

655
00:31:31,846 --> 00:31:33,366
Why didn't you tell me just now?

656
00:31:33,766 --> 00:31:37,846
Think about your family and yourself.

657
00:31:38,085 --> 00:31:40,126
Strive for a lighter sentence.

658
00:31:41,366 --> 00:31:44,565
You're supposed to tell me
important clues as such

659
00:31:44,565 --> 00:31:48,805
so that I can try my best to plead for your sake.

660
00:31:54,805 --> 00:31:56,205
That's all I have to ask.

661
00:31:57,846 --> 00:31:59,726
This is a POA.

662
00:31:59,766 --> 00:32:02,565
Your family already signed it before this.

663
00:32:02,886 --> 00:32:05,685
Sign it and confirm it again.

664
00:32:06,366 --> 00:32:07,766
From now on,

665
00:32:08,445 --> 00:32:11,366
I will act as your official attorney.

666
00:32:24,006 --> 00:32:26,006
Thank you for making the trip.

667
00:32:28,006 --> 00:32:29,445
(I already met Hu Dewang.)

668
00:32:29,646 --> 00:32:30,925
(He'll follow my instructions.)

669
00:32:31,325 --> 00:32:32,726
That's great.

670
00:32:33,766 --> 00:32:34,966
I have to rely on experts like you

671
00:32:35,205 --> 00:32:37,325
to deal with such situations indeed.

672
00:32:39,846 --> 00:32:41,805
(But you mustn't transfer
the money to my bank card.)

673
00:32:42,646 --> 00:32:43,445
Don't worry.

674
00:32:43,526 --> 00:32:44,445
I won't.

675
00:32:44,846 --> 00:32:46,766
I've instructed someone else
to transfer it to your wife's bank card.

676
00:32:47,766 --> 00:32:48,565
(Thank you.)

677
00:32:48,646 --> 00:32:49,966
(Tell me if you need anything else.)

678
00:32:52,726 --> 00:32:55,126
My lawyer's license was canceled
temporarily after all.

679
00:32:55,246 --> 00:32:56,606
It's inconvenient for me to act.

680
00:32:56,685 --> 00:32:58,766
Please help me out in the future.

681
00:33:00,285 --> 00:33:00,846
By the way,

682
00:33:02,246 --> 00:33:03,325
regarding this matter...

683
00:33:04,526 --> 00:33:06,045
(Don't worry. I won't tell anyone.)

684
00:33:08,685 --> 00:33:11,165
Mr. Jin, you're intelligent indeed.

685
00:33:11,325 --> 00:33:12,165
I didn't even need to tell you.

686
00:33:12,886 --> 00:33:13,366
That's right.

687
00:33:14,085 --> 00:33:15,445
Please don't tell anyone about it.

688
00:33:31,486 --> 00:33:33,165
You look ugly when you frown.

689
00:33:37,165 --> 00:33:38,486
At least she won't be executed.

690
00:33:39,526 --> 00:33:40,366
Don't worry.

691
00:33:40,805 --> 00:33:41,766
I'm still here for you.

692
00:33:42,805 --> 00:33:43,405
Thank you.

693
00:33:49,580 --> 00:33:53,580
(Five years ago)

694
00:33:54,925 --> 00:33:56,966
Xin, I'm penniless now!

695
00:33:57,085 --> 00:33:58,726
I've lost all of my money!

696
00:33:59,205 --> 00:34:00,126
Look at you.

697
00:34:00,846 --> 00:34:04,085
Before this, debt collectors were chasing after you.

698
00:34:04,685 --> 00:34:05,486
Who helped you?

699
00:34:06,045 --> 00:34:07,526
I helped you.

700
00:34:07,846 --> 00:34:08,966
I lent you money

701
00:34:09,006 --> 00:34:10,286
so that you could survive.

702
00:34:10,806 --> 00:34:11,445
But look,

703
00:34:12,125 --> 00:34:13,086
you didn't keep your promise.

704
00:34:13,165 --> 00:34:15,165
You took my kindness for granted.

705
00:34:15,726 --> 00:34:17,326
And now, you actually tried to escape.

706
00:34:18,726 --> 00:34:20,326
I had to spend so much effort
to locate you.

707
00:34:20,806 --> 00:34:23,365
Do you think that's
the right thing to do?

708
00:34:26,685 --> 00:34:27,526
No!

709
00:34:28,006 --> 00:34:28,766
Xin!

710
00:34:28,845 --> 00:34:29,605
I know my fault now!

711
00:34:30,365 --> 00:34:31,286
Please give me a chance!

712
00:34:33,046 --> 00:34:34,566
I didn't say I wasn't going
to give you a chance.

713
00:34:35,966 --> 00:34:37,726
Your debt isn't that huge anyway.

714
00:34:38,046 --> 00:34:39,845
It's just 500,000 yuan.

715
00:34:40,246 --> 00:34:40,925
Xin!

716
00:34:41,125 --> 00:34:42,486
I'm truly penniless now!

717
00:34:42,726 --> 00:34:43,286
Besides,

718
00:34:43,405 --> 00:34:46,925
my family didn't know that I came here to gamble!

719
00:34:47,046 --> 00:34:48,645
I'll have no way to face my family

720
00:34:48,966 --> 00:34:49,645
if they hear about this!

721
00:34:49,645 --> 00:34:50,286
Quiet!

722
00:34:51,726 --> 00:34:52,365
You're so noisy.

723
00:34:53,165 --> 00:34:53,966
Kai?

724
00:34:55,086 --> 00:34:56,365
You can't even deal with
a nobody like him?

725
00:34:56,405 --> 00:34:57,006
Mister!

726
00:34:58,526 --> 00:34:59,125
Kai!

727
00:34:59,685 --> 00:35:00,685
What are you doing?

728
00:35:00,885 --> 00:35:02,566
This is none of your business.

729
00:35:02,605 --> 00:35:03,806
Go upstairs.

730
00:35:08,526 --> 00:35:09,286
Hurry.

731
00:35:22,885 --> 00:35:23,486
Fine.

732
00:35:23,885 --> 00:35:24,766
You guys can deal with him.

733
00:35:25,405 --> 00:35:26,125
Remember.

734
00:35:26,885 --> 00:35:28,246
Keep him alive.

735
00:35:28,445 --> 00:35:28,966
Xin!

736
00:35:29,365 --> 00:35:30,125
Don't leave me here!

737
00:35:30,766 --> 00:35:31,205
Xin!

738
00:35:38,885 --> 00:35:39,605
Here's the IOU.

739
00:35:40,486 --> 00:35:41,165
All done.

740
00:35:45,726 --> 00:35:46,286
Here.

741
00:35:46,605 --> 00:35:47,526
You can keep it.

742
00:35:47,885 --> 00:35:49,006
It's the same if you keep it.

743
00:35:52,006 --> 00:35:53,645
I prepared some dishes today.

744
00:35:53,766 --> 00:35:54,925
All of them are your favorite.

745
00:35:55,086 --> 00:35:56,845
But I don't know if they're nice or not.

746
00:35:57,405 --> 00:35:58,845
They're definitely not as nice
as the food we have back home.

747
00:36:01,046 --> 00:36:01,645
By the way,

748
00:36:02,445 --> 00:36:03,645
when are you heading back?

749
00:36:07,205 --> 00:36:09,645
Security's been pretty tight lately.

750
00:36:11,445 --> 00:36:14,286
I've prepared a card for you.

751
00:36:15,445 --> 00:36:16,286
Take it.

752
00:36:17,205 --> 00:36:19,605
Tell me if you need more money.

753
00:36:21,605 --> 00:36:22,365
What do you mean?

754
00:36:22,925 --> 00:36:23,845
Are you chasing me away?

755
00:36:25,006 --> 00:36:25,885
Nonsense.

756
00:36:26,605 --> 00:36:28,086
Why would I try to chase you away?

757
00:36:28,766 --> 00:36:31,645
It's just that I came upon
an opportunity lately.

758
00:36:32,766 --> 00:36:33,845
I wish to grab hold of it.

759
00:36:34,286 --> 00:36:35,845
That person can lead us

760
00:36:36,205 --> 00:36:38,165
to the life we desire.

761
00:36:39,566 --> 00:36:40,205
What about you then?

762
00:36:41,165 --> 00:36:42,086
Will you leave with me?

763
00:36:44,165 --> 00:36:45,365
I can't.

764
00:36:46,046 --> 00:36:46,966
I have my mission to fulfill.

765
00:36:48,885 --> 00:36:50,165
We're no longer young.

766
00:36:51,246 --> 00:36:52,766
We can't do this forever.

767
00:36:54,286 --> 00:36:55,006
Kai,

768
00:36:55,645 --> 00:36:57,165
I know you've been enduring it
for a long time.

769
00:36:57,286 --> 00:37:00,205
But we'll realize our goals soon.

770
00:37:00,766 --> 00:37:02,445
We'll be able to lead
the life we desire.

771
00:37:03,165 --> 00:37:05,445
I know you've endured it for many years.

772
00:37:05,645 --> 00:37:06,566
All this while,

773
00:37:07,006 --> 00:37:08,086
you've been complaining about

774
00:37:08,405 --> 00:37:09,566
why you have to learn this

775
00:37:09,605 --> 00:37:11,125
and that and improve yourself

776
00:37:11,165 --> 00:37:12,566
when you're in this trade.

777
00:37:13,006 --> 00:37:13,845
But you need to know

778
00:37:14,086 --> 00:37:16,526
that you're doing so to help me out.

779
00:37:17,925 --> 00:37:19,205
I don't care about that.

780
00:37:20,165 --> 00:37:21,445
I just want to be with you.

781
00:37:22,205 --> 00:37:23,286
Every day.

782
00:37:24,165 --> 00:37:25,405
That's why I will do the things

783
00:37:26,086 --> 00:37:26,925
you want me to do.

784
00:37:29,086 --> 00:37:29,766
I understand.

785
00:37:30,966 --> 00:37:31,726
I promise.

786
00:37:32,645 --> 00:37:33,726
That day will come soon.

787
00:37:34,845 --> 00:37:36,445
Since I've already made you a promise,

788
00:37:37,006 --> 00:37:38,326
I'm sure you know me well.

789
00:37:38,766 --> 00:37:40,205
I'm a woman of my promise.

790
00:37:40,766 --> 00:37:42,246
However, I've also promised A

791
00:37:43,205 --> 00:37:44,885
that we will accomplish

792
00:37:44,925 --> 00:37:46,566
our common goal together.

793
00:37:46,685 --> 00:37:47,405
It's A again?

794
00:37:48,326 --> 00:37:49,605
You always talk about A.

795
00:37:50,246 --> 00:37:51,445
I've never seen him before.

796
00:37:51,966 --> 00:37:53,286
I don't know the kind of person he is.

797
00:37:53,885 --> 00:37:55,246
Why should I obey his instructions?

798
00:37:55,365 --> 00:37:56,566
Why should I risk my life for him?

799
00:37:56,766 --> 00:37:57,486
What gives?

800
00:37:57,845 --> 00:37:58,445
Kai,

801
00:37:59,086 --> 00:38:00,806
I'll tell you this once again.

802
00:38:01,246 --> 00:38:02,885
You have to believe in A

803
00:38:03,165 --> 00:38:04,365
and protect him.

804
00:38:04,966 --> 00:38:06,046
As long as he's around,

805
00:38:06,086 --> 00:38:08,645
there's hope for everything.

806
00:38:09,605 --> 00:38:10,365
Besides,

807
00:38:10,845 --> 00:38:12,006
you've never met him before.

808
00:38:12,165 --> 00:38:13,566
You don't understand him at all.

809
00:38:13,685 --> 00:38:15,685
His capability far exceeds what you can imagine.

810
00:38:16,685 --> 00:38:17,566
So, listen to me.

811
00:38:18,566 --> 00:38:19,566
Believe in him, okay?

812
00:38:21,165 --> 00:38:22,086
I don't believe in him.

813
00:38:26,006 --> 00:38:26,925
But I believe in you.

814
00:38:42,726 --> 00:38:45,405
These are the summaries
of the interrogations, evidence,

815
00:38:45,645 --> 00:38:47,605
defense arguments,
and prosecution opinion I've prepared.

816
00:38:47,605 --> 00:38:48,086
(Jiangcheng People's Procuratorate,
Notary Opinion Letter)

817
00:38:48,086 --> 00:38:48,726
Mr. Wang,

818
00:38:48,845 --> 00:38:50,046
please check them for me.

819
00:38:56,205 --> 00:38:57,486
Seems like I'm getting old.

820
00:38:59,726 --> 00:39:01,326
I don't think I can help you out here.

821
00:39:01,925 --> 00:39:02,766
Mr. Wang,

822
00:39:02,806 --> 00:39:04,726
you must be joking with me.

